snippet.title: Border 2 Tribute Trailer में Sunny Deol-Mona Singh के एक सीन से फिल्म का बड़ा सीक्रेट खुल गया!
snippet.description:
The Cinema Show | Episode 1331| January 21

In this episode of The Cinema Show, we will discuss upon the new tribute trailer of Border 2. A big secret of the film has been revealed in this new trailer even before the film's release. We will also talk about Vicky Kaushal’s cameo in Dhurandhar 2. Along with this, we will share how public is reacting to  Shahid Kapoor starrer O Romeo trailer.
